DataTableAjaxLinkPanel
public abstract class DataTableLinkPanel<T>
extends org.apache.wicket.markup.html.panel.Panel
implements org.apache.wicket.markup.IMarkupResourceStreamProvider, org.apache.wicket.markup.IMarkupCacheKeyProvider

Panel containing a link in text or icon form, for the execution of an action on a DataTable. The action is executed using a plain link, making this implementation suitable for downloading a file.
